'''Ṣaḥriǧ''' d yiwet n tɣiwant n [[Tmurt n Leqbayel]] id yezgan deg twilayt n [[Tubiret]]. Tezga-d 50.3 Km ar ugmuḍ n Tubiret, 73.1 Km ar wunẓul n Tizi Wezzu d 104 Km seg umalu n [[Bgayet]], tennulfa-d deg unegzun anemhal n 1984. 

Taɣiwant n Ṣaḥriǧ tettwassen s yimjahden-is i wwten uẓẓal ɣef uzarug n [[Ledzayer]]. Diɣ teqṛeb idurar n [[Ǧerǧer]].

